ntor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A taxa de reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes, tamb\u00e9m conhecida como taxa de reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes ou customer retention rate em ingl\u00eas, \u00e9 uma m\u00e9trica que mede a porcentagem de clientes que continuam fazendo neg\u00f3cios com uma empresa durante um per\u00edodo espec\u00edfico, em compara\u00e7\u00e3o com o n\u00famero total de clientes no in\u00edcio desse per\u00edodo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a84260c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a84260c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dad591d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"dad591d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Por que a taxa de reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes \u00e9 importante?<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a523a81 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a523a81\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2bd0513 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2bd0513\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Redu\u00e7\u00e3o de custos:<br \/><\/strong>A aquisi\u00e7\u00e3o de novos clientes \u00e9 geralmente mais cara do que manter clientes existentes. Investir na reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes pode ser uma estrat\u00e9gia mais econ\u00f4mica a longo prazo, uma vez que custa menos do que conquistar novos clientes continuamente.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-298ff74 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"298ff74\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e2241c elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3e2241c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Maior lucratividade<br \/><\/strong>Clientes fi\u00e9is tendem a gastar mais com a empresa ao longo do tempo. Eles s\u00e3o mais propensos a fazer compras repetidas, comprar produtos ou servi\u00e7os adicionais e recomendar a empresa a outras pessoas, o que aumenta a lucratividade.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aab0b4c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"aab0b4c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1a1f95 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1a1f95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Constru\u00e7\u00e3o de rela\u00e7\u00f5es duradouras:<br \/><\/strong>A reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes permite que as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.socialhub.pro\/\">empresas<\/a> construam relacionamentos duradouros com seu p\u00fablico. Essas rela\u00e7\u00f5es podem se traduzir em uma base de clientes leais que continuam a apoiar a empresa ao longo dos anos.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d683303 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d683303\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c33af9 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4c33af9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Feedback valioso:<br \/><\/strong>Clientes fi\u00e9is muitas vezes fornecem feedback valioso que pode ser usado para melhorar produtos, servi\u00e7os e a experi\u00eancia geral do cliente. Essas informa\u00e7\u00f5es s\u00e3o fundamentais para o aprimoramento dos neg\u00f3cios.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05cadd4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"05cadd4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8dc5045 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8dc5045\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Resist\u00eancia \u00e0 concorr\u00eancia:<br \/><\/strong>Clientes leais s\u00e3o menos propensos a serem influenciados pela concorr\u00eancia e a migrar para outras empresas. Isso cria uma vantagem competitiva sustent\u00e1vel.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1781574 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1781574\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6fd9c0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b6fd9c0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Como melhorar a taxa de reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes?\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-102239f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"102239f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd1405f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cd1405f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Entenda as necessidades dos clientes:<br \/><\/strong>Conhecer e entender as necessidades, desejos e expectativas de seus clientes \u00e9 fundamental. Realize pesquisas, colete feedback e analise dados para personalizar sua abordagem e atender \u00e0s expectativas do cliente.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a287442 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a287442\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">