ner\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Como funciona a taxa de reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes?<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-239d04e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"239d04e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-96e22a4 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"96e22a4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A taxa de reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes \u00e9 uma m\u00e9trica que mede a porcentagem de clientes que permanecem fi\u00e9is a uma <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">empresa<\/a> ao longo de um per\u00edodo espec\u00edfico, em compara\u00e7\u00e3o com o n\u00famero total de clientes no in\u00edcio desse per\u00edodo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c57a9cb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c57a9cb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ddb0e92 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ddb0e92\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Ela \u00e9 calculada subtraindo-se o n\u00famero de novos clientes adquiridos do n\u00famero de clientes no final do per\u00edodo e, em seguida, dividindo pelo n\u00famero de clientes